  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized controlled study evaluating the impact of 2 months of oral appliance
      therapy on endothelial function in patients with severe obstructive sleep apnea syndrome
      intolerant to continuous positive airway pressure (CPAP) therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
